project.name: SNEP
project.description: SNEP is a Brazilian Free Software-based PBX that meets the needs of any size of business, with features that make communication more free, flexible and intelligent. Snep has a GPLv2 license and all its code is in https://bitbucket.org/snepdev/snep-3 and your download can be done in https://sourceforge.net/projects/snep/.  Web Interface to manage asterisk and more.
